metadata.name: SABC Weekly 2022 Review
metadata.description: Compilation of the 2022 weekly covers from Sketchy Ape Book Club (SABC) given to the community. Huge thanks to BEAUTIFULvoid who faithfully created each weekly cover. Much appreciation to Sketchy Degens, Sketchy Labs & Sketchy Ape Book Club communities.  Biggest thanks to the original Sketchy artist HashLips!
